{"tid":788650,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屌係咪個撚個女人都要日撚日買嘢","createTime":"2018-08-21T15:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T18:02:14.000Z","uid":4322,"like":14,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"65b282c7960a4ecb83eb96389893ddfe88e9b0b8","tid":788650,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 fg份糧已經唔係多 平時又唔撚會儲錢<br />\n叫你儲錢=慘過去死！<br />\n叫你投資又要嫌唔方便 又要嫌回報低<br />\n屌你回報高咪風險高囉仆街 你又唔撚係識投資！<br />\n<br />\n個撚個禮拜都要買衫！<br />\n咩好撚抵呀 上網一次買幾件好平！<br />\n仆街 件件咪一鳩樣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話你又唔鍾意 <br />\n唔話你又過唔到自己個關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呀仆你個街 個死人銀包用咗唔夠半年<br />\n開始每晚都嫌佢細又唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初就係你話夠細先方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家想點撚樣先？<br />\n&ldquo;襯屋企人下個月去法國定意大利買銀包會有平&rdquo;<br />\n買個名牌銀包！可以裝多好多嘢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口吻仲要咁理所當然！<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打救我！可以點引導佢儲吓錢呀屌！<br />\n唔好話中出即飛thx!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6facf8582df3f5a1b9a86611dfc90c96a7a4a8","tid":788650,"uid":92123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:46:13.000Z","msg":"你有諗過同佢有將來咩？<br />\n冇既話 儲唔儲錢有咩關係"},{"pid":"9b444248484f7bc94b58b9dc70b22ee9f3be26ab","tid":788650,"uid":4322,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1f6facf8582df3f5a1b9a86611dfc90c96a7a4a8","tid":788650,"uid":92123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:46:13.000Z","msg":"你有諗過同佢有將來咩？<br />\n冇既話 儲唔儲錢有咩關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"就係有先要煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303fa9f05d26ad0c5cdc3356ef542e36e5f97412","tid":788650,"uid":9603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15: